Package: rmdwc
Type: Package
Title: Word, Character and Non-Whitespace Character Counts in R Markdown Documents Including and Excluding Code Chunks
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2020-08-22
Authors@R: 
  c(person("Sigbert", "Klinke", email="sigbert@hu-berlin.de", role=c("aut", "cre")))
Description: If you are using R Markdown documents then you have sometimes restrictions about the size of the documents, e.g. number of words, number of characters or non-whitespace characters. rmdcount() computes these counts and returns the result as data frame.
Imports: knitr
